text: Vanessa Agbortabi (born 4 December 1998) is a German volleyball player. == Career == She participated in the 2015 FIVB Volleyball Girls' U18 World Championship, 2017 FIVB Volleyball Women's U20 World Championship, and the 2018 FIVB Volleyball Women's Nations League. == References == == External links == * FIVB profile * CEV profile * * * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:German women's volleyball players Category:People from Main-Taunus-Kreis
